Revision history for YAML-Tiny-Color

0.04    2014-06-30 (SHARYANTO)

        - Workaround for Scalar::Util 1.39 change to looks_like_number()
          (booleanize the result). Use (temporary?) replacement
          Scalar::Util::LooksLikeNumber.


0.03    2012-11-22 (SHARYANTO)

        - dep: Specify minimum version for Term::ANSIColor (BRIGHT_GREEN etc not
          yet specified in older version).


0.02    2012-11-16 (SHARYANTO)

        - Tweak colors a bit (null becomes BOLD).


0.01    2012-11-16 (SHARYANTO)

        - First release. Based on YAML::Tiny 1.51.
